
        0 1 2 3 4 ---> Left to Right  [size = 0 to length-1]
        _ _ _ _ _
name = |H|A|R|R|Y|  (length = 5)
        - - - - -
       -5-4-3-2-1 <--- Right to Left

String : Data type in python, String is a sequence of characters enclosed in quotes.
1. Single - '...'
2. Double - "..."
3. Triple - '''...'''

****
Slicing
-------
Syntax:
s1 = name[index_start : index_end : step]

Eg:
s1 = name = [0:3] --> Har

skip:Syntax:
word = "amazon"

Eg:
word = [1:7:2] --> mzn